1
00:01:10,680 --> 00:01:11,280
Gu Haoran.

2
00:01:14,039 --> 00:01:14,560
Ziqing.

3
00:01:20,440 --> 00:01:21,560
I just went to the bathroom,

4
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:22,080
and then

5
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:23,700
