6
00:01:33,240 --> 00:01:34,560
Keep drinking.

7
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:41,259
What are you doing?

8
00:01:42,520 --> 00:01:43,400
Gu Haoran.

9
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:46,759
I don't know what's wrong with me lately.

10
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:48,880
I feel like

11
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:52,100
I'm starting to like you a little.

12
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,200
You like me?

13
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:03,120
Ziqing.

14
00:02:04,720 --> 00:02:05,780
What are you doing?

15
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:15,140
Ziqing!

16
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:17,980
Ziqing!

17
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:21,860
Ziqing!

18
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:26,040
Ziqing!

19
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:26,880
You...

20
00:02:32,640 --> 00:02:33,100
Ziqing!

21
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:53,200
Dad, Mom.

22
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:55,360
Didn't I tell you?

23
00:02:55,920 --> 00:02:57,480
I drank too much that day.

24
00:02:58,000 --> 00:02:58,880
Mr. Gu.

25
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:01,340
No matter what, since this happened,

26
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:03,820
the Gu Group must give us an explanation.

27
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:05,100
In this matter,

28
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:07,010
my grandson is in the wrong.

29
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:10,160
But since they love each other,

30
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:14,040
why don't they get officially engaged now?

31
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:16,120
Engaged?

32
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:17,280
The Gu family

33
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:19,740
will give 13.14 million as a bride price.

34
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:22,050
The Haitian Shengyan Villa

35
00:03:22,440 --> 00:03:23,640
will be used as the marital home

36
00:03:23,640 --> 00:03:25,320
and transferred to your daughter

37
00:03:25,320 --> 00:03:26,579
to show our sincerity.

38
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:28,730
As expected of you, sir,

39
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:30,280
