40
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:30,760
Dad.

41
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:32,680
No, it's settled.

42
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:33,740
Listen to your dad.

43
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:35,760
Then we'll go home and prepare.

44
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:39,760
The engagement banquet will be held at Longguo Hotel this afternoon.

45
00:03:39,760 --> 00:03:40,280
Okay.

46
00:03:40,520 --> 00:03:41,400
Okay.

47
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:43,920
Are we really getting married?

48
00:03:43,920 --> 00:03:45,760
Then we won't bother you anymore.

49
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:46,290
Goodbye.

50
00:03:46,440 --> 00:03:46,720
Okay.

51
00:03:46,720 --> 00:03:47,360
Let's go.

52
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:50,480
I...

53
00:03:51,200 --> 00:03:52,040
Hurry up.

54
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:58,860
I'm sorry, sir.

55
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,080
It's my fault.

56
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,480
Haoran and Ziqing

57
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,960
had a hard time sparking as it is.

58
00:04:04,440 --> 00:04:05,560
After all this,

59
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:07,760
you actually helped Haoran out.

60
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:09,240
However,

61
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:11,020
I still need to remind you.

62
00:04:11,640 --> 00:04:14,320
Ziqing is now Haoran's fiancée.

63
00:04:15,040 --> 00:04:16,640
You need to know your limits.

64
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:17,880
Don't go too far.

65
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:33,960
Hello,

66
00:04:34,320 --> 00:04:34,840
Shiqi.

67
00:04:35,440 --> 00:04:36,480
Is the file decrypted?

68
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:37,280
Yes, Captain.

69
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:38,880
The decrypted content shows that

70
00:04:38,880 --> 00:04:40,760
Zixi has found out who the mastermind is.

71
00:04:40,760 --> 00:04:41,420
It turns out

72
00:04:41,640 --> 00:04:42,880
the International Racing Alliance has been

73
00:04:42,880 --> 00:04:44,760
hindering the development of new energy racing cars.

74
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:45,360
That is why

75
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:46,760
they have been secretly

76
00:04:46,760 --> 00:04:48,290
sabotaging the TG project.

77
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:51,480
I've uncovered a lot of shady deals lately.

78
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:52,920
The mastermind behind all this

79
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:53,960
is Mr. S.

80
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:55,600
It's him.

81
00:04:56,760 --> 00:04:57,480
Zixi, he

82
00:04:57,520 --> 00:04:58,760
is trying to kill us.

83
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:00,400
Recently,

84
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:02,960
during the development of the TG new energy racing project,

85
00:05:02,960 --> 00:05:04,220
an accident occurred,

86
00:05:04,400 --> 00:05:06,720
and the chief designer, Song Haoming, resigned and took the blame.

87
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:08,250
It seems my guess was right.

88
00:05:09,440 --> 00:05:11,040
The whole story connects.

89
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:13,080
How about this, Shiqi?

90
00:05:13,080 --> 00:05:13,960
Notify Baozi.

91
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:16,280
Let's meet up tonight if we have time.

92
00:05:16,280 --> 00:05:17,940
I want to reorganize the team.

93
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:19,160
Reorganize the team?

94
00:05:19,400 --> 00:05:19,930
Captain.

95
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:21,920
But you are Gu Haoran now.

96
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:24,970
Don't worry about that.

97
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:27,050
I will use Gu Haoran's identity

98
00:05:27,080 --> 00:05:28,800
to participate in the Dragon Country Grand Prix

99
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:30,680
and challenge for the championship.

100
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:31,210
This way,

101
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:34,159
the mastermind behind the International Racing Federation

102
00:05:34,159 --> 00:05:35,620
will naturally come to me.

103
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:52,360
Young master.

104
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:54,000
The guests have all arrived.

105
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:55,080
Got it.

106
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:56,520
I'm going upstairs now.

107
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:57,080
Okay.

108
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,560
Everyone is waiting.

109
00:06:05,080 --> 00:06:05,920
Help!

110
00:06:06,520 --> 00:06:07,400
Help!

111
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:09,080
Help!

112
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:12,880
Sir.

113
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:15,880
Sir.

114
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:17,330
Are you alright?

115
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:20,200
Sir,

116
00:06:20,640 --> 00:06:21,720
