117
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:23,920
I'll take you to the hospital.

118
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:24,320
Come.

119
00:06:28,280 --> 00:06:29,080
Young Master,

120
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,970
