121
00:06:31,080 --> 00:06:32,600
I just met an old man in the basement

122
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:33,860
who had a heart attack.

123
00:06:34,520 --> 00:06:36,180
I brought him to the hospital.

124
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:37,440
Hurry up.

125
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:39,680
Almost there. We'll be there soon.

126
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:40,340
Godfather.

127
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:41,060
Godfather.

128
00:06:43,320 --> 00:06:44,120
Jingchi.

129
00:06:44,960 --> 00:06:45,720
Henan.

130
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:51,340
Godfather.

131
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:52,800
Are you all right?

132
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:53,420
Doctor.

133
00:06:54,080 --> 00:06:55,540
How is my godfather doing?

134
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:57,960
Thanks to this gentleman bringing the patient here in time,

135
00:06:57,960 --> 00:06:59,020
he is out of danger.

136
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:09,050
Are you feeling better?

137
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:11,720
Young man,

138
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:14,320
thank you so much for saving me.

139
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,120
What's your name?

140
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:17,760
He is...

141
00:07:18,080 --> 00:07:19,210
My name is Gu Haoran.

142
00:07:23,840 --> 00:07:24,920
I am Shi Chen.

143
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:28,180
This is my adopted son,

144
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:29,720
Vincent.

145
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:31,520
Vincent.

146
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:37,920
Thank you,

147
00:07:38,840 --> 00:07:39,440
Mr. Gu.

148
00:07:48,080 --> 00:07:48,720
Mr. Shi,

149
00:07:49,159 --> 00:07:50,560
I have things to do, so I'll get going.

150
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,560
Please rest well.

151
00:07:55,880 --> 00:07:56,360
Vincent.

152
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:57,020
Godfather.

153
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:59,200
Help me see Mr. Gu out.

154
00:07:59,400 --> 00:08:00,400
Okay, Godfather.

155
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:06,930
Captain.

156
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:11,360
It's been five years.

157
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,560
How have you been?

158
00:08:14,840 --> 00:08:17,040
I only heard about Zixi later.

159
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:19,280
You've got the wrong person.

160
00:08:19,280 --> 00:08:20,480
I'm not your captain.

161
00:08:21,960 --> 00:08:22,490
Captain.

162
00:08:23,840 --> 00:08:24,570
Don't worry.

163
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:27,960
Whatever your reason is for changing your name,

164
00:08:27,960 --> 00:08:29,200
I won't tell anyone.

165
00:08:30,960 --> 00:08:32,690
I guess I should thank you then.

166
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:34,500
I didn't mean it like that.

167
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:37,970
Let's pretend we never met.

168
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:51,560
Mr. Gu,

169
00:08:51,680 --> 00:08:52,680
