170
00:08:53,040 --> 00:08:54,160
Where is Gu Haoran?

171
00:08:55,160 --> 00:08:55,690
Mr. Chen,

172
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:57,090
have some tea first.

173
00:08:57,240 --> 00:08:58,240
He has some things

174
00:08:58,440 --> 00:08:59,440
that delayed him.

175
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:02,000
Chairman,

176
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:03,440
I just asked the young master,

177
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:05,080
and he said he'll be here soon.

178
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:05,940
Still waiting?

179
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:07,860
How long do we have to wait?

180
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:09,600
It's so late.

181
00:09:11,160 --> 00:09:11,760
He's here.

182
00:09:11,880 --> 00:09:12,610
Uncle, Aunt,

183
00:09:12,880 --> 00:09:13,680
I'm very sorry

184
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:15,090
to keep you waiting.

185
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:20,040
Haoran is not usually like this.

186
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:20,840
This time,

187
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:22,880
there must be something important

188
00:09:22,880 --> 00:09:23,880
that delayed him.

189
00:09:23,920 --> 00:09:24,780
Right, Luo Xin?

190
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:26,360
Yes, Miss Chen.

191
00:09:26,520 --> 00:09:27,040
Ziqing.

192
00:09:27,160 --> 00:09:28,420
Stop speaking for him.

193
00:09:29,040 --> 00:09:32,120
What could be more important than getting engaged today?

194
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:33,600
It seems the reputation of our Chen family

195
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:34,600
is not big enough.

196
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:37,640
You're exaggerating, Mr. Chen.

197
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:39,840
How could my brother dare to slight you?

198
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:41,050
Come on, Haoran,

199
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:42,680
drink three bottles as a penalty

200
00:09:42,680 --> 00:09:44,140
and apologize to Mr. Chen.

201
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:46,800
You,

202
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:47,960
hurry up.

203
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:50,400
Three bottles of Maotai.

204
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,930
Are you trying to drink me to death?

205
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:20,490
Mr. Chen.

206
00:10:20,680 --> 00:10:22,880
I am Assistant Zhao from Taichen Group.

207
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:23,840
Hello.

208
00:10:24,160 --> 00:10:24,680
Hello.

209
00:10:24,920 --> 00:10:26,600
The chairman asked me to inform you

210
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:28,040
that Taichen Group has decided

211
00:10:28,040 --> 00:10:30,000
to invest in Chen Group's new project.

212
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:31,330
At 10:00 a.m. tomorrow,

213
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:32,720
please come to our group headquarters

214
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:35,120
to discuss specific cooperation details.

215
00:10:35,520 --> 00:10:36,080
Okay.

216
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:37,360
Thank you.

217
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:38,920
Our Chen Group

218
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:40,850
will not let your company down.

219
00:10:42,040 --> 00:10:42,970
You are welcome.

220
00:10:43,240 --> 00:10:45,200
This is all for the sake of Mr. Gu.

221
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:46,930
Understood.

222
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:53,040
This Gu Haoran really kept his abilities hidden.

223
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:56,280
Taichen had always refused to invest in us before.

224
00:10:56,280 --> 00:10:58,320
Now they agreed because of this kid.

225
00:11:02,800 --> 00:11:03,280
Haoran.

226
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:06,240
We will be family in the future.

227
00:11:06,480 --> 00:11:07,920
Being late is a minor thing.

228
00:11:07,920 --> 00:11:09,120
Don't worry about it.

229
00:11:09,640 --> 00:11:11,840
My father-in-law is very reasonable.

230
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:16,970
Mr. Chen.

231
00:11:17,280 --> 00:11:18,320
You're not angry anymore?

232
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:19,450
Why would I be angry?

233
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:21,160
My son-in-law is so busy.

234
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:23,560
It's normal for him to be a little late.

235
00:11:23,560 --> 00:11:24,160
It's fine.

236
00:11:24,320 --> 00:11:25,000
It's fine.

237
00:11:27,520 --> 00:11:28,440
Come, in-law.

238
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:30,240
I was out of line just now.

239
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:31,640
I'll punish myself with three bottles.

240
00:11:31,640 --> 00:11:32,240
Mr. Chen.

241
00:11:33,040 --> 00:11:33,160
Congcong.

242
00:11:33,160 --> 00:11:33,820
Have a seat.

243
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:35,680
Three glasses are enough.

244
00:11:35,680 --> 00:11:36,400
Okay.

245
00:11:37,280 --> 00:11:38,210
Then bottoms up.

246
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:39,080
Uncle,

247
00:11:39,800 --> 00:11:40,520
I'll join you for three glasses.
